NHANES Variable Codebook

SEQN = Respondent ID
RIAGENDR = Gender
RIDAGEYR = Age in years
RIDRETH3 = Race/Ethnicity
DMDEDUC2 = Education Level
BMXBMI = Body Mass Index
BMXWT = Weight (kg)
BMXHT = Height (cm)
PAQ605 = Moderate Activity
PAQ620 = Vigorous Activity
PAD680 = Minutes Sedentary
Activity_Level = Created activity category variable
